{"tid":1131894,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙利：歐聯席位好重要咩？","createTime":"2019-04-30T02:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T03:07:47.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2ba0379b528262dba46ed067363fc034c1d22c","tid":1131894,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】時近季尾，歐聯席位爭奪戰進入直路，但車路士領隊沙利卻指，是傳媒誇大了它的重要性。<br />\n歐聯這個歐洲最高殊榮的賽事，獎金極豐，而且是不少球員夢寐以求出戰的舞台，但曾兩度帶領拿玻里出戰歐聯的沙利（Maurizio Sarri）表示：「我認為歐聯的重要性是傳媒吹捧出來。」<br />\n他的理據是這個賽事需要運氣：「當然這是一個在歐洲甚至全世界都很重要的賽事，但要踢得非常好，同時要有運氣，才能夠身處其中。」<br />\n車路士現時有兩個機會在來季重返歐聯，一是殺入英超前4，二是贏得歐霸盃冠軍。他們在聯賽現排第5位，跟第4位的阿仙奴同得66分，比第6位的曼聯多2分；於歐霸盃4強則將鬥法蘭克福。<br />\n沙利坦言不會在二選一，但表明希望贏得歐霸盃：「不是為了晉身歐聯，全因這是重要的賽事。」"},{"pid":"dc107362a079eb87b5c8bb783d1e2ca98ed2fda9","tid":1131894,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"煙蛇所言甚是"},{"pid":"c4f28a81e035e4eccab0d357bae6db58571e222a","tid":1131894,"uid":247666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"躝啦仆街 用契仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46345c36d51308e1d2c66176f348f0d4faedc844","tid":1131894,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"歐洲霸主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe46cfd531ad51d92c57fdda37949cd1505acab","tid":1131894,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"歐聯奬金呀<br />\n你唔好出人工吖笨"},{"pid":"96df3a9b52298c0e0dfe95e8dd4b6cbda70838bf","tid":1131894,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"最少 有錢分先 <br />\n唔入歐聯 邊同到第二個聯賽班霸踢過 較量吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}